title: Microorganisms
description: An illustration depicting various types of microorganisms. The image features four distinct shapes: a blue amoeba-like organism with a red nucleus, a green elongated organism with a tail, a purple spiral-shaped organism, and a blue oval-shaped bacterium with internal structures visible. Each microorganism is stylized and colorful, showcasing the diversity of microscopic life.

title: Seaweed on the Shore
description: A piece of brown seaweed is washed up on a sandy beach, partially covered by gentle waves. The texture of the seaweed contrasts with the smooth, light-colored sand.
